, now a publisher will show. Try to publish with `aPub2` and now it publishes, as well as `aPub3`.\r\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create publisher <code>aPub</code> to topic <code>A</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create publisher <code>aPub2</code> to topic <code>A</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Destroy <code>aPub</code> and do <code>gz topic -i A</code>, no publishers will show. Try to publish with <code>aPub2</code> and it doesn't publish.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create publisher <code>aPub3</code> to topic <code>A</code> and do <code>gz topic -i A</code>, now a publisher will show. Try to publish with <code>aPub2</code> and now it publishes, as well as <code>aPub3</code>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2015-11-12T02:18:30.032303+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:43:47.761970+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1782}